{"tid":1686088,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【會師中環】點解冇「藍色經濟圈」 - 神仙丁","createTime":"2019-11-01T02:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T07:15:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":66,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9679d363c5dffe1dca23a23555aa6a4055443fec","tid":1686088,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191101/L7IYEU45FB6UW3BEIPYPAN4OZI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191101%2FL7IYEU45FB6UW3BEIPYPAN4OZI%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=a36bd7bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191101%2FL7IYEU45FB6UW3BEIPYPAN4OZI%2F&h=b20ec7a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191101/L7IYEU45FB6UW3BEIPYPAN4OZI/</a><br />\n<br />\n【會師中環】點解冇「藍色經濟圈」 - 神仙丁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/WrAf4Zrm8GJG1U4V-nPFPLRovWs=/802x531/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/IYF7FZW6D6ZTNS7YGXR4DLIQ3A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FWrAf4Zrm8GJG1U4V-nPFPLRovWs%3D%2F802x531%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FIYF7FZW6D6ZTNS7YGXR4DLIQ3A.jpg&h=cbfad21c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藍色商店富臨，近月生意慘淡。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\nauthor<br />\n專欄作家 : 神仙丁<br />\n<br />\n近日有市民發起「黃色經濟圈」，希望以不停幫襯的方式「懲罰」支持社運的商店，同時罷買親政府舖頭。行動的確有效，依筆者所見，有黃色商店大排長龍，藍色商店則明顯比以前冷清。藍色商店如優品360、富臨表現如此慘淡，為何反社會運動的不去支持一下，實行「逼爆」藍色商店？<br />\n<br />\n第一個理由與建制陣營的人數有關，就是反運動的人數比黃色陣營明顯地少，這亦反映於各大民調之中，比例有「7:3」甚至是「8:2」，根本就沒有「買爆」的本錢。在日常衣食住行方面，人數就是一切，就算你有錢人，所食的都不過是一人份量，你可以憑一人之力「食窮」富臨嗎？況且，有錢人都應該不會食富臨。<br />\n<br />\n另外，民調亦顯示政府支持者，普遍為年紀較大及學歷較低人士。這班人收入相對較低 ，購買力不高，而且亦較欠缺行動力。再講，這個群組的人接收資訊的渠道較窄，未必會上網，隨時連黃店藍店都分不清 。<br />\n<br />\n最後，撐黃店某程度是有少許代價的，例如你要搜集資料、行遠啲、排耐啲，市民之所以會繼續做，是因為有理念支持。而現時仍撐政府的人，其理念都是「收成期」、「有着數」，說穿了就是自己利益行先，自然不會額外付出去支持無生意的藍店。<br />\n<br />\n神仙丁<br />\n《審計搵丁》負責人<br />\n<a href=\"http://facebook.com/AuditSlave/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FAuditSlave%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvEKa%2BtsrA1nil%2BMmquCK26s%3D&h=173197e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/AuditSlave/</a><br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"ca36583e58fd9d3f5715e188de3023f5a5179851","tid":1686088,"uid":160257,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:28:18.000Z","msg":"堅持黃經濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30447b858c8026e71ee9b0ae45b56395f68a8ad2","tid":1686088,"uid":24862,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:38:36.000Z","msg":"建立黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ab9b1f7aab4a545df992468f0735531ab557b6","tid":1686088,"uid":249794,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:40:52.000Z","msg":"簡而精<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6485d994d9b25b0cc8f6c17d6a95edfc4dbd7cc","tid":1686088,"uid":130695,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:43:36.000Z","msg":"所以唔明仲有班人話針對藍屍廢老做文宣<br />\n跟本有利益班垃圾自然痴埋黎<br />\n到時叫佢死撚開佢都爭住奶啦"},{"pid":"38dccf2ac2912b4214da451debcb98376f8aa4d6","tid":1686088,"uid":197540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"Agree"},{"pid":"75c3ab4463fae2224f8a51db796c0d21988b146f","tid":1686088,"uid":202345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:45:38.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"b10f6ff1e16230ed4cf8ec53ac8b7219cd9fbe78","tid":1686088,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T02:49:35.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈係長期抗爭"},{"pid":"cabaaf912dd1f2760f542e22f563e88ba4a4a1b6","tid":1686088,"uid":1945